description:
In this video, I go on a shopping spree for some of the rarest and most unique gaming consoles from Japan using Sendico. From colorful GameCube to failed Apple experiments, I unbox a ton of retro gaming history - though getting them all working proves to be a challenge. Join me as I explore these forgotten gems and see if they were worth importing after all these years.

Subscribe for more! https://www.youtube.com/austinevans
